<h3> The Entry Level Build </h3>

<p style="color: white;"> This is for the person who has some more money to spare, and wants to get serious with gaming.<br>
This build can handle 1080p high/ultra settings in most games. For this build, don't forget to to get a BIOS flash  kit for new Raven Ridge CPUs like the Ryzen 3 2200G<br>
and Ryzen 5 2400G </p>


