<h3> The Casual Build </h3>

<p style="color: white;"> This build is for people who are getting serious about gaming or work and media production. It can play games at 1440p at medium settings with ease.<br>
The 6 core 12 thread Ryzen cpu really helps with multitasking and bigger workloads. </p>

